quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,82,"Rárá. Wọ́n máa tako ìjọ́sìn wọn, wọ́n si máa di ọ̀tá wọn."
  19,83,"Ṣé ìwọ kò wòye pé dájúdájú Àwa ń dẹ àwọn èṣù sí àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ ni, tí wọ́n sì ń gùn wọ́n gan-an (síbi ẹ̀ṣẹ̀)?"
  19,84,"Nítorí náà, má ṣe kánjú nípa (ìyà) wọn. A kúkú ń ka (ọjọ́) fún wọn ní kíkà tààrà."
  20,64,"Nítorí náà, ẹ kó ète yín jọ papọ̀ mọ́ra wọn. Lẹ́yìn náà, kí ẹ tò wá ní ọ̀wọ̀ọ̀wọ́. Dájúdájú ẹni tí ó bá borí ní òní ti jèrè.”"
  20,65,"(Àwọn òpìdán) wí pé: “Mūsā, ìwọ ni o máa kọ́kọ́ ju (ọ̀pá sílẹ̀ ni) tàbí àwa ni a óò kọ́kọ́ jù ú sílẹ̀.”"
  20,66,"(Mūsā) sọ pé: “Ẹ ju (tiyín) sílẹ̀ (ná).” Nígbà náà ni àwọn okùn wọn àti ọ̀pá wọn bá ń yíra padà lójú rẹ̀ nípasẹ̀ idán wọn, bí ẹni pé dájúdájú wọ́n ń sáré."
  21,40,"Ṣùgbọ́n (ìyà Iná) yóò bá wọn ní òjijì, nígbà náà ó máa kó ìdààmú bá wọn; wọn kò sì níí lè dá a padà. A kò sì níí sún (ìyà náà) síwájú fún wọn."
  21,41,"Wọ́n kúkú ti fi àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ kan ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ ṣíwájú rẹ! Nítorí náà, ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ sì dìyà tó yí àwọn tó ń fi wọ́n ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ po."
  21,42,"Sọ pé: “Ta ni ẹni tí ó ń ṣọ yín ní òru àti ní ọ̀sán níbi ìyà Àjọkẹ́-ayé?” Àmọ́ ńṣe ni wọ́n ń gbúnrí kúrò níbi ìrántí Àjọkẹ́-ayé."
  22,16,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ ní àwọn āyah tó yanjú. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń tọ́ ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́ sí ọ̀nà."
  22,17,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo àti àwọn tó di yẹhudi àti àwọn sọ̄bi’ūn àti àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ àti àwọn mọjūs àti àwọn tó ṣẹbọ, dájúdájú Allāhu yóò ṣèdájọ́ láààrin wọn ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Arínú-róde gbogbo n̄ǹkan.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:62 àti ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yūnus; 10:90.]
  22,18,"Ṣé o ò wòye pé dájúdájú Allāhu ni àwọn tó ń bẹ nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti àwọn tó ń bẹ lórí ilẹ̀, àti òòrùn, òṣùpá, àwọn ìràwọ̀, àwọn àpáta, àwọn igi, àwọn n̄ǹkan ẹlẹ́mìí àti ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ nínú àwọn ènìyàn ń forí kanlẹ̀ fún? Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ sì ni ìyà ti kò lé lórí. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá fi àbùkù kàn, kò sí ẹnì kan tí ó máa ṣe àpọ́nlé rẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń ṣe ohun tí Ó bá fẹ́.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah ar-Ra‘d; 13:15.]
